sequenceDiagram
    participant L as Learner
    participant UI as Next.js Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant DB as Database
    participant ML as ML Model

    L->>UI: Types code / clicks buttons
    UI->>UI: Buffer keystroke events (1.5s)
    UI->>API: POST /events/batch
    API->>DB: Store events

    opt Webcam Enabled
        UI->>UI: FaceMesh extracts features (2s)
        UI->>API: POST /webcam/batch
        API->>DB: Store webcam features
    end

    loop Every 3 seconds
        UI->>API: GET /load/{session_id}
        API->>DB: Query last 10s of events + webcam
        API->>API: Aggregate features
        API->>ML: predict_load(features)
        ML-->>API: score, label, confidence, action
        API-->>UI: LoadEstimateOut
        UI->>UI: Update gauge + adapt UI
    end

    L->>UI: Submit solution
    UI->>API: POST /problems/submit
    API->>API: Run tests via Node.js subprocess
    API->>DB: Store submission result
    API->>API: Select next problem based on load
    API-->>UI: SubmissionOut + next_problem_id

    L->>UI: Rate effort (1-7)
    UI->>API: POST /labels/effort
    API->>DB: Store ground truth label
